<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="51" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,866,1252]" pageId="7" pageNumber="51">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,288,986,1012]" pageId="7" pageNumber="51">Female</emphasis>
. Total length ca. 4.0. Head: antennae dark brown, with 
<number box="[937,966,986,1012]" pageId="7" pageNumber="51" value="14.0">14</number>
unicolorous flagellomeres. Thorax dark brown; coxae dark brown; fore and midleg femora and tibiae pale yellow; hind femur pale yellow at basal 
<number box="[151,205,1066,1092]" pageId="7" pageNumber="51" value="0.33">0.33</number>
, the rest reddish brown; hind tibia dark brown; tibial spurs formula 
<number box="[999,1012,1066,1092]" pageId="7" pageNumber="51" value="1.0">1</number>
: 
<number box="[1016,1036,1066,1092]" pageId="7" pageNumber="51" value="2.0">2</number>
: 
<number box="[1041,1061,1066,1092]" pageId="7" pageNumber="51" value="2.0">2</number>
. Wing without apical dark spot; length ca. 
<number box="[272,312,1106,1132]" pageId="7" pageNumber="51" value="2.5">2.5</number>
; Sc ending free. Halter white. Abdomen dark brown, without pale yellow bands.
</paragraph>
